      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Content</head>
         <p>The card files for a collection of books on handwriting. The book collection has been classified and cataloged for the General Library, and various departmental libraries (primarily Psychology). The card files are arranged in two alphabetical sequences: Authors, A-Z; Subjects, A-Z.</p>
         <p/>
      </scopecontent>
